WHO   — Mohg, Lord of Blood — the Omen who chose the Formless Mother
WHAT  — Morgott's Omen twin, who answered the same rejection with heresy and rose as the Lord of Blood.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the underworld — the sewers of his youth and the Mohgwyn dynasty's palace deep underground  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — He stole the slumbering Miquella from his cocoon to be the Mohgwyn dynasty's god — a rival order founded on cursed blood.
HOW   — Sworn to the Formless Mother, the Outer God of blood, he wields bloodflame and builds a dynasty in a palace deep underground.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Where one twin knelt to the Order that cursed him, the other bled himself a new god.

